Name: System and Software Engineering Standards
Documentation:
It is a tool for systems and software engineering standards. It contains an overview of the relevant standards.

Use cases:
- User wants to read description of the standard on the website of the creator
- User wants to know which standards exist on which topics in the environment

This view was created on February 25th, 2020 and updated on March 26th, 2020.
Creator: alexander.efremoff@gmail.com
